---
const videoId = 'oZMcvmsDMi4'
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gold tracking-widest mb-2">MOVIE</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy">テスト英語塾を紹介する動画</h2>
      <p class="text-ink/65 mt-3">サービスの詳細や実際のレッスン風景をご覧ください</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-navy/10 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(8,17,38,0.16)]" style="aspect-ratio: 16/9;">
      <iframe
        src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${videoId}?rel=0`}
        title="テスト英語塾 紹介動画"
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
